data.description: Welcome Home! This stunning popular Hudson floor plan offers 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Built in 2020, this 2764 square feet home is sure to impress. The open floor plan features a gas fireplace with mantel, hardwood floors on main level, and tile flooring in the bathrooms. Enjoy the eat-in kitchen, spacious center island, tile backsplash, craftsman trim, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom features 2 separate walk-in closets, double vanities, amazing oversized tiled shower with two shower heads and bench. Main floor front office space with custom accent wall. Beautiful backyard with covered patio, fenced in yard and additional deck which is great for grilling and entertaining.  Take advantage of the community amenities, including a playground and pool. FREE re-finance within 3 years if Buyer uses preferred lender and title company.
